pic Games</a>已从<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fortnite"><em>《堡垒之夜》</em></a>的锦标赛模式中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/chains-of-hades-removed-from-fortnite-tournament-after-doja-cat-rages-against-the-weapon-3757180">删除了最近添加的 Chains Of Hades 武器</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/rockstar-denies-delay-rumours-for-grand-theft-auto-6-3757193">Rockstar 否认了《侠盗猎车手 6》推迟发售的传闻，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
